HEADWORD: Registry
<hw>Reg"is*try</hw> <pr>(r?j"?s*tr?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act of recording or writing in a register; enrollment;
registration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The place where a register is kept.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A record; an account; a register.</def> <rj><au>Sir
W. Temple.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Regius</ent>⟦br⟧
